18:43.330 --> 18:44.786
Oh.

18:44.790 --> 18:45.870
Food!

18:45.880 --> 18:47.416
Them...

18:47.420 --> 18:48.409
take!

18:48.420 --> 18:49.569
No, no, no, no.

18:49.580 --> 18:50.877
