[Maddie] Look, we want
to help you.

18:58.170 --> 19:00.206
-[screaming]
-Whoa!

19:03.210 --> 19:04.495
Hey, calm down!

19:04.500 --> 19:06.240
-[hissing]
-Whoa!

19:06.250 --> 19:07.285
[hisses]

