[both screaming]

19:20.460 --> 19:21.495
Hey!

19:25.250 --> 19:27.241
Ryn! Water!

19:27.250 --> 19:28.660
Now!

19:28.670 --> 19:30.285
No.

19:47.420 --> 19:49.376
