19:51.330 --> 19:54.959
My sister not bad.

19:54.960 --> 19:56.746
It's her instinct.

19:56.750 --> 19:57.819
That's all.

19:57.830 --> 19:59.036
She was confused.

19:59.040 --> 20:01.372
Yeah, of course,
she was confused.

20:01.380 --> 20:05.032
She sided with you
instead of her own sister.

20:05.040 --> 20:07.702
Have you two ever fought
like that before?

20:07.710 --> 20:09.029
No.

20:09.040 --> 20:11.918
Yeah, she felt betrayed.

20:11.920 --> 20:13.535
It's unnatural.

20:13.540 --> 20:15.076
They don't belong here.

20:15.080 --> 20:17.457
You're only here
because those fishermen

20:17.460 --> 20:19.496
