from the water.

20:19.500 --> 20:22.116
And God knows what
the military did to her.

20:22.120 --> 20:23.872
Sister was hurt.

20:23.880 --> 20:27.281
A man took her blood,

20:27.290 --> 20:28.666
her skin.

20:28.670 --> 20:29.989
I'm sorry.

20:30.000 --> 20:32.491
For her, people are bad.

20:32.500 --> 20:34.286
No trust.

20:34.290 --> 20:35.917
[Ben] There are
a lot of bad people.

20:38.830 --> 20:40.457
Maybe even my own family.

20:40.460 --> 20:41.870
Ben, we don't know
if that's true.

20:41.880 --> 20:43.324
We do know that.
Xander said it.

20:43.330 --> 20:44.615
They're out fishing
night and day,

20:44.620 --> 20:46.076
