20:51.000 --> 20:52.820
We are gonna figure it out.

20:52.830 --> 20:54.536
We're gonna stop it.

20:54.540 --> 20:56.781
What about the sister?

20:56.790 --> 20:59.327
Sh_e's out there
roaming the streets.

20:59.330 --> 21:02.208
Do you think your sister
went back to the ocean?

21:02.210 --> 21:03.996
No.

21:04.000 --> 21:07.538
Will not go without me.

21:07.540 --> 21:10.498
Blood will bring shark.

21:10.500 --> 21:12.536
She need place to...

21:12.540 --> 21:14.371
-To heal?
-Yes.

21:14.380 --> 21:17.031
But will come for me.

21:17.040 --> 21:19.247
I'm thinking it'd be
a whole lot safer
at the houseboat.

21:19.250 --> 21:20.410
Yeah, for sure.

21:20.420 --> 21:21.956
