21:27.880 --> 21:29.108
[laughing]

21:32.120 --> 21:35.533
-Ooh! Hey, Listen...
-[man 2] Look at that.

21:35.540 --> 21:36.495
Go Whalers!

21:36.500 --> 21:37.956
-[hisses]
-Whoa!

21:37.960 --> 21:40.372
[men laughing]

21:40.380 --> 21:42.166
Yeah, girl.

21:43.210 --> 21:45.371
[ominous music playing]

21:55.580 --> 21:57.377
[sniffing]

22:03.750 --> 22:05.160
[hisses]

22:13.960 --> 22:16.201
Hey! What are you
doin' in here?!

22:16.210 --> 22:17.416
Get away from there!

22:18.420 --> 22:20.069
Stupid meth heads.

22:23.830 --> 22:25.161
You can't do that!

22:27.960 --> 22:29.450
[hisses]

22:30.620 --> 22:32.167
[hisses]

22:32.170 --> 22:34.616
Holy jeez!

22:34.620 --> 22:36.372
[growling shriek]

22:40.170 --> 22:41.489
[Wally screams and grunts]

22:43.670 --> 22:44.455
[hisses]

22:46.620 --> 22:48.417
[bell ringing, alarm sounding]

23:02.580 --> 23:04.286
Hey, Dad.

23:04.290 --> 23:05.325
Thanks.

23:05.330 --> 23:06.615
What happened?

23:06.620 --> 23:08.201
Hey. Yeah,
thank you very much.

23:08.210 --> 23:10.075
Okay, listen to this.
Some, half-naked girl

23:10.080 --> 23:11.786
tried to eat the catch
right out of the bins.

23:11.790 --> 23:14.452
Then she beat the hell
out of Wally Merton.

23:14.460 --> 23:15.700
-Big Wally?
-Yeah?

23:15.710 --> 23:17.575
Why?

23:17.580 --> 23:20.743
I have no idea. I guess
he was trying to stop her.

23:20.750 --> 23:22.456
That's a new one.

23:26.670 --> 23:28.535
So, where do you
want to start?

23:28.540 --> 23:31.327
I was thinking I'd take
the day to get up to speed.

23:31.330 --> 23:32.490
